    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Branch of mathematics that deals with the collection and arrangement of numerical facts or data,whether relating to human affairs or to natural phenomena.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
